cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CL, cs.CY 

This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and specifically on the problem of efficiently learning from crowdsourced data. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also touches on topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CY), as these fields often rely on labeled data and can benefit from efficient crowdsourcing methods.
